The paper deals with image inpainting, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework is also applicable to robotics and autonomous systems, as it can be used for vision-based robot localization purposes (cs.RO). The use of deep learning and generative models suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to graphics (cs.GR) due to its focus on generating realistic images.
